      "updated": 1783537455380,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Unit Test\n    - small, fast tests that verify business or technical functionality.\n    - They are fast because:\n            - they are not allowed to touch a network, filesystem, database, etc.\n            - they should be \"pure functions\"\n    - obviously not EVERYTHING can be covered with a unit test.\n\n    - Usually one assert per test - (just a \"smell\" - try to keep them focused)",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Unit Test\n    - small, fast tests that verify business or technical functionality.\n    - They are fast because:\n            - they are not allowed to touch a network, filesystem, database, etc.\n            - they should be \"pure functions\"\n    - obviously not EVERYTHING can be covered with a unit test.\n\n    - Usually one assert per test - (just a \"smell\" - try to keep them focused)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "TAObUSL7SawQZuVdRLNxy",
      "type": "text",
