      "updated": 1783537569576,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Test-Driven Development -\n    But you are using this to \"design\" (CAFO) what you are building.\n    Thinking through it as you go. \n\n\nTest-First Development - write the test before you write the code, \n    quit writing the code when the test passes, basically.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Test-Driven Development -\n    But you are using this to \"design\" (CAFO) what you are building.\n    Thinking through it as you go. \n\n\nTest-First Development - write the test before you write the code, \n    quit writing the code when the test passes, basically.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
