      "updated": 1783537929298,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Write horrible stupid code that passes.\ntime it. Don't take too long. Find your number\n(mine is in C# three minutes, in Rust, it's longer, etc)\nIf you don't have the test passing in X minutes, delete the\ntest and think of another one you can do in X minutes.\n\"BS\" - Bullcrap code that isn't \"real\" to make the test pass.\n(Gary Bernhardt calls it \"sliming\") - your next test(s)\nshould help you get rid of that \"slime\". ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Write horrible stupid code that passes.\ntime it. Don't take too long. Find your number\n(mine is in C# three minutes, in Rust, it's longer, etc)\nIf you don't have the test passing in X minutes, delete the\ntest and think of another one you can do in X minutes.\n\"BS\" - Bullcrap code that isn't \"real\" to make the test pass.\n(Gary Bernhardt calls it \"sliming\") - your next test(s)\nshould help you get rid of that \"slime\". ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
