      "text": "\"Global Day of Code Retreat\"\n\nAs many 45 minute sessions as you can fit in a day.\n\n- delete the code\n- get another partner\n- start over\n\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "\"Global Day of Code Retreat\"\n\nAs many 45 minute sessions as you can fit in a day.\n\n- delete the code\n- get another partner\n- start over\n\n",
